column3: Deliver the muu shuwuu eggs to Jenkshi.
I have heard you successfully followed in Bardam's footsteps. This must mean you are capable of flight, yes? Because I require the aid of such an individual.
My sheep has fallen ill and I need the eggs of a muu shuwuu in order to treat her.
However, I cannot obtain one of their eggs on my own. Muu shuwuu build their nests in high places and I am yet to conquer Bardam's Mettle.
Please, bring me three eggs. My flock's lives depend on it!
Please, bring me three muu shuwuu eggs. My flock's lives depend on it!
Were you able to get three eggs for me? My sheep does not have long left!
This disease spreads quickly if not dealt with early on. I could not bear the idea of losing a single sheep, never mind the whole flock.
It shall not be easy, but I too must conquer Bardam's Mettle if I am to look after my flock on my own. Thank you for your help this time, my sheep would be done for without you.
